Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just about a year ago when we\Nhad our entrance ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Class 1-A"     "Class 1-B"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just about a year ago when we\Nhad our entrance ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Class 1-A"     "Class 1-B"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Our class assignments were stuck\Nto the bulletin boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Our class assignments were stuck\Nto the bulletin boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And among the crowd of new students,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,there was one other girl keeping her distance\Nfrom the crowd, just like myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl who exchanged glances with me then\Njust happened to be Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, back then, I had\Nabsolutely no interest in strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I even hoped that she'd stop looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A year had passed, and now, Shimamura\Nand I were both second-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Does God actually exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something that could\Nhear my voiceless prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class again.\NHow many years has it been now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,About ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like almost everyone else\Ngot split up. Like Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.97,0:01:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If we end up in separate classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura probably wouldn't come to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably wouldn't mind\Nif I came to see her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But she wouldn't come to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't think Shimamura\Nactually needs me that badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Class 2-B"\N"Sakura Adachi"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely not a decent\Nperson worth any praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.05,0:01:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine that I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,enough good deeds to be\Nrewarded with anything I ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Does God actually exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something that could\Nhear my voiceless prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Sakura Adachi"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish and I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I stand tall, searching for that name...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yippee! Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Hogetsu Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I started my second year in high school
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and my hair color went\Nback to its natural color.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In my new class,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,my seat and most of my classmates had changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but Adachi still remained right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So your first name is Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I ever ask you that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you prefer Miss Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I mean... Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I was just looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi... Why are you following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, that's what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:05:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so much like a puppy sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Woof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll go get my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually like dogs quite a bit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never get over how big her house is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Roll, roll, roll, roll, roll, roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of the tatami is just so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I changed, just like you asked.\NThis is what you wanted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute, Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first thought to cross my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then. I guess I'll get changed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning to spend the night\Nat your place today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Spend the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your place is huge,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured no one would notice\Neven if I stayed over. Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously... You should've asked me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'd object if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Tae, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I sure am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, your name is Taeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're already changed.\NPlease come greet our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why do I have to greet them, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're a part of this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is exactly why\NI hate coming home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Shimamura, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Hey, wanna have lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, come on. Come sit with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come this way, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't bring my lunch,\Nso I'm going to go buy something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So have you guys been friends for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, just since this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in any clubs, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in concert band.\NThe number of members is a bit iffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They all introduced themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but they talked too fast\Nand I couldn't understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was something like\NPancho, Sancho, and Delos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured they must be some kind\Nof traveling comedy troupe. JK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that those\Nwere actually their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, their idle chatter continued, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to remember what they\Nwere talking about, but just couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:09:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to the café by the station now.\NWant to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Their pancakes are super yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a cute little shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh... Sorry, I can't today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our classes changed and now that\NHino and Nagafuji were gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made new artificial friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Hino and Nagafuji\Nwere at least entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But we weren't so close\NI'd go out of my way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to hang out with them now\Nthat our classes were different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't keep up with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really hold onto relationships\Nand that might make me coldhearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But here's how I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so very few strong relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that flow along with you\Ndown this river of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"When should I return the notes I borrowed?"\N"The next time we see each other is fine."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"When should I return the notes I borrowed?"\N"The next time we see each other is fine."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The longer you stay in this river of fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Thanks."\N"I haven't seen..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The longer you stay in this river of fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the more bonds weaken, and eventually break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi stopped showing up to class
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the following Monday after the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I go have a peek?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's what Adachi's waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I go up there and a teacher spots us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, are you close with Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, she's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured. I saw you two talking all\Nthe time last year. Is she sick today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So I went to the same middle school\Nas Adachi, but she's totally changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I mean, she still didn't\Ntalk to anyone in class,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but she seemed even more guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if any of that has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, there's something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't feel so... standoffish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, she doesn't\Nseem so prickly anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, when I interact with Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,she doesn't bother with the thorns\Nand just stiffens and curls up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi's rejection wasn't even that strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't go check the second floor of the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tarumi"\N"Incoming Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey... Um, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna hang out sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll try harder this time. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so things don't end up as awkward as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I don't know if you need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Yeah, we're going to hang out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. How about next Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Heck yeah! I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Miss... Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured this was a better attitude to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you prefer hanging out with someone calmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is worth looking into...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At least she's decisive about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this is paradise...\NHaving such a big bath is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer the one at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd call it being frugal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I like smaller houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see. Wanna trade homes then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... Yeah, that'd be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like anything would\Nchange here even if I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I'd let you touch\Nthem once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You like them, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so generous, aren't I? But don't\Nmove your fingers around too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's enough, tha--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are cute, Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you really do like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen once we see each other?\NI probably shouldn't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that when I go out with Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you're early!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Adachi's about the only person\Nwho'd rush over in a Chinese dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, was I laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I'm not late, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I just came too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so, uh... Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Oh, right. I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You always laughed like that, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima, you've gotten sexier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't think of the words...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I wanted to say...\NYou've gotten bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't think you need to\Npush this being super excited thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. At least half of it is genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"{\i1}Okonomiyaki{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this exhausting for your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think stuff like this\Nis important... Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hear you've been responsible lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom calls my mom sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They only talk to each other\Nsuper rarely, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They go so long without speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to hear that from\Nyou personally, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's partially the reason why\NI invited you out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, my goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be a nicer way to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked about our recent events while\Nmaking sure our {\i1}okonomiyaki {\i0}didn't burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru is surprisingly observant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If this were Adachi, I spaced out and\Nimagined she'd probably burn the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how much whatever Taru was\Nsaying wasn't getting through to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly am a coldhearted person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I was physically facing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,there was still a part of me\Nkeeping its distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to say that you're my acquaintance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Acquaintance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That I've known for a while...\NAnd now I'm here in front of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I even saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where are we going next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's a little shop over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they sell random knickknacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, they have a lot of straps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we buy matching ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you like? I'll match mine\Nwith whatever one you pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you actually put it on your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something to worry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling you'd lose it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, that's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean... You don't really\Nget attached to people or things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm worried that you\Nmight not take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take good care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your expression\Nis really vague right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Vague?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But whenever I see your profile with\Nsuch a vague expression on your face
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what you're actually thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be possible to hang out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be friends again, Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why she invited me out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have located Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,S-See you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru has always been like that, and in\Nthe past, I was able to keep up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think that maybe\NI'm the odd one out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:21:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What even am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just you, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.\NYou actually can be useful at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,--Two weeks after our first term started...\N--So, yesterday, I went to club\Nfor the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,--As usual, I went to my classes,\Nbought bread at the student store,\N--So, yesterday, I went to club\Nfor the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--As usual, I went to my classes,\Nbought bread at the student store,\N--That's rare.\N--They were awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,--and ate lunch with my artificial friends.\N--Oh, it's that third-year, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,--I just kept doing the same thing\Nover and over.\N--Yeah, Yamada.\N--Being in a club is sort of a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,--The only thing that was different...\N--Yeah, Yamada.\N--Being in a club is sort of a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,--...was Adachi wasn't in front of me.\N--They're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Relationships are so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, on our way home,\Nwanna get pancakes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Shi--?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After Sancho, and Taru,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,this was the third time someone\Ncalled me since April started.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the third time really is the charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 10: 'Cherry Blossoms and\NSpring and Spring and the Moon'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, it was finally Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.55,0:22:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 10: 'Cherry Blossoms and\NSpring and Spring and the Moon'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'The Moon and Determination,\NDetermination and Friends'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'The Moon and Determination,\NDetermination and Friends'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: New school term.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.97,0:23:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'The Moon and Determination,\NDetermination and Friends'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.97,0:23:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the same class as you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'The Moon and Determination,\NDetermination and Friends'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's act like we've never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:23:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:24:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so lovely and mature, Miss Nagafuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're oh so cute, Miss Hino.
